reviewText: Loved it when I was a kid -- the horse race & horse are great. Remembered the race scenes as being much longer. Still worth the watch.

i love both Natalie Wood and Barbara Stanwyck.  Both beautiful Cancer women,  but of course Natalie Wood was a child in this movie.
this movies was best of both worlds.
Fun little film for a rainy afternoon. Nice performance (as always) by Barbara Stanwyck, and it is fun to see a young Natalie Wood.
